text.tspan: Ranking nodes to define a set

flowRoot.flowPara: In addition to Fourier approach we plan to use DCTWT Daubechies wavelets. It aims to distinguish revelant nodes by reducing unusual values of nodes.
Each final point of monitoring, formelly a value, are now consider as a nodes. We mesh all the nodes to all each others to design an undistiguished graph.
We plan to use Google PageRank sum algorithm to identify most revelant nodes in the mesh. Once all node ranked, we will select a set revelant nodes.
Supposed unrevelant node or not yet ranked node we be tagged in families. It aims to allow dynamic commission and decommision of nodes between trainning phase and usage of non supervised AI.
